78
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:59,920
What? You know him?

79
00:04:00,160 --> 00:04:01,640
I couldn't know him better.

80
00:04:01,720 --> 00:04:03,359
He's just a demon.

81
00:04:23,960 --> 00:04:25,560
Li Bugui

82
