85
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:34,120
soon after his birth

86
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:36,440
and only he survived by a miracle.

87
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:38,280
Since then,

88
00:04:38,280 --> 00:04:40,039
he has begun to hide

89
00:04:40,160 --> 00:04:41,200
and learn martial arts.

90
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:42,280
Meanwhile, he became

91
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:45,160
so brutal.

92
00:05:02,520 --> 00:05:04,960
Then he killed the master of the Lingxiao Sect,

93
00:05:05,320 --> 00:05:06,840
