94
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:08,440
and became the sect's new master.

95
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:10,680
Then he became more rampant

96
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:11,520
and bloodthirsty.

97
00:05:11,960 --> 00:05:14,000
No matter who

98
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:15,480
insulted him,

99
00:05:16,080 --> 00:05:17,800
